Package: duckknit
Title: A Knitr Engine for DuckDB CLI
Version: 0.0.9.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Colin", "Rundel", , "rundel@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a knitr chunk engine that interfaces with the DuckDB
    command-line interface. Chunks can target specific database files and
    maintain persistent sessions across chunks within a document.
URL: https://rundel.github.io/duckknit/,
    https://github.com/rundel/duckknit
BugReports: https://github.com/rundel/duckknit/issues
